high_descs: Turn to your right and walk to the white table.
grab the salt shaker from the table.
Approach the black end table to the left.
Place the salt shaker on the black end table.
Walk back to the white table on the right.
Grab the salt shaker from the white table.
Approach the black end table to the left.
Place the salt shaker on the black end table.
anns.task_desc: Place two salt shakers on the black end table.

high_descs: Turn to the right and walk forward to face the table.
Pick up the salt on the left side of the table.
Step to the left and face the black table at the end of the counter.
Place the salt shaker on the bottom right corner of the black table.
Take a step to the right to face the table.
Pick up the remaining salt shaker on the table.
Step to the left to face the black table.
Place the salt shaker on the black table behind the first salt shaker
anns.task_desc: To move both salt shakers from the white table to the black table.

high_descs: Walk forward and then turn to your right so you face the table
Pick up a salt from off of the table
Take a step back to face the black table
Put the salt on the black table
Go back to where you were standing previously
Pick up the pepper from off of the table
Take a step back again to face the black table
Set the pepper down next to the salt
anns.task_desc: Move the salt and pepper from the counter to a table
